Doesn’t Ben Mendelsohn get tried of playing villains? I’m certainly tired of seeing him in another villain role. (He was particularly awful as the Sheriff of Nottingham in the recent “Robin Hood”).

body:
Becoming A Man

Billy: I wish I could be a big kid super hero like you guys, but I don’t know how!

Wally: Allow us to demonstrate. First, puff out your chest.

Billy: Okay. *puffs out his chest*

Wally: Great, now say, “Tax Exemption!”

Billy: Tax Exemption!

Dick: Now you must acquire a taste for Freeform Jazz!

*the three sit and listen to jazz for a few moments, all in various thinking positions*

Dick: Okay Billy, you’re ready!
